{"total":3,"pageSize":10,"pageCount":1,"data":[{"title":"Research","slug":"Research","author":"Huaqiang","date":"2020-05-10T08:31:57.000Z","updated":"2020-05-10T03:46:48.435Z","comments":true,"pin":null,"path":"api/articles/Research.json","excerpt":"","keywords":null,"cover":"http://img5.imgtn.bdimg.com/it/u=3395038082,2027547865&fm=15&gp=0.jpg","content":"<link rel=\"stylesheet\" class=\"aplayer-secondary-style-marker\" href=\"\\assets\\css\\APlayer.min.css\"><script src=\"\\assets\\js\\APlayer.min.js\" class=\"aplayer-secondary-script-marker\"></script><div style=\"float:left;border:solid 1px 000;margin:2px;\"><img src=\"http://img5.imgtn.bdimg.com/it/u=3395038082,2027547865&fm=15&gp=0.jpg\"></div>\n\n<ol>\n<li>Nucelar materials</li>\n<li>Ion beam analysis</li>\n<li>Accelerator</li>\n</ol>\n<link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"/css/spoiler.css\" type=\"text/css\"><script src=\"/js/spoiler.js\" type=\"text/javascript\" async></script>","text":" [Figure] Nucelar materialsIon beam analysisAccelerator","link":"","raw":null,"photos":[],"categories":[{"name":"Research","slug":"Research","count":1,"path":"api/categories/Research.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"Research","slug":"Research","count":1,"path":"api/tags/Research.json"}]},{"title":"晶界对辐照缺陷的吸收","slug":"晶界对辐照缺陷的吸收","author":"Huaqiang","date":"2019-09-30T08:31:57.000Z","updated":"2020-05-10T06:40:35.536Z","comments":true,"pin":null,"path":"api/articles/晶界对辐照缺陷的吸收.json","excerpt":"","keywords":null,"cover":"https://warmshawn.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/groupweb/mogb1000x400.png?x-oss-process=style/style1","content":"<link rel=\"stylesheet\" class=\"aplayer-secondary-style-marker\" href=\"\\assets\\css\\APlayer.min.css\"><script src=\"\\assets\\js\\APlayer.min.js\" class=\"aplayer-secondary-script-marker\"></script><div style=\"float:left;border:solid 1px 000;margin:2px;\"><img src=\"https://warmshawn.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/groupweb/mogb1000x400.png?x-oss-process=style/style1\"></div>\n\n<p>晶界是一种特殊的界面，可以作为缺陷阱，为辐照产生的缺陷提供湮灭的场所。</p>\n<link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"/css/spoiler.css\" type=\"text/css\"><script src=\"/js/spoiler.js\" type=\"text/javascript\" async></script>","text":" [Figure] 晶界是一种特殊的界面，可以作为缺陷阱，为辐照产生的缺陷提供湮灭的场所。","link":"","raw":null,"photos":["http://warmshawn.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/Science/XRD_av_3_5nm_As-deposited.png?x-oss-process=style/style1"],"categories":[{"name":"Tech - Q","slug":"Tech-Q","count":2,"path":"api/categories/Tech-Q.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"Grain Boundary","slug":"Grain-Boundary","count":1,"path":"api/tags/Grain-Boundary.json"}]},{"title":"辐照对柔性材料的电学性能调控","slug":"辐照对柔性材料的电学性能调控","author":"Huaqiang","date":"2019-09-30T08:31:57.000Z","updated":"2020-05-10T06:38:00.781Z","comments":true,"pin":null,"path":"api/articles/辐照对柔性材料的电学性能调控.json","excerpt":"","keywords":null,"cover":"https://warmshawn.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/groupweb/fanyongpaper1.jpeg?x-oss-process=style/style1","content":"<link rel=\"stylesheet\" class=\"aplayer-secondary-style-marker\" href=\"\\assets\\css\\APlayer.min.css\"><script src=\"\\assets\\js\\APlayer.min.js\" class=\"aplayer-secondary-script-marker\"></script><div style=\"float:left;border:solid 1px 000;margin:2px;\"><img src=\"https://warmshawn.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/groupweb/fanyongpaper1.jpeg?x-oss-process=style/style1\"></div>\n\n<p><br><br>自2012年以来，摩擦电纳米发电机（TENG）由于其普遍适用性强，成本低，效率高逐渐成为机械能量收集和分布式微能源领域的主流技术。TENG的发展可以服务于物联网的信息采集技术、智能监控系统以及静电驱动、静电除尘等高电压应用领域。TENGs中的摩擦起电材料是决定其性能的核心要素，而探寻一种高效且长期稳定的改性材料的方法是目前必须要克服的困难。</p>\n<p>针对这一问题，北京纳米能源所的陈翔宇研究员与北京大学物理学院的付恩刚教授合作，提出了一种通过低能高密度氦离子的辐照来操纵聚合物的摩擦电表面电荷密度的实验方法。近期，他们在Energy &amp; Environmental Science 上发表了题为 “Manipulating the triboelectric surface charge density of polymers by low-energy Helium ion irradiation/implantation”的论文。</p>\n<p>论文链接</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://pubs.rsc.org/en/content/articlelanding/2020/ee/c9ee03307f/unauth#!divAbstract\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">https://pubs.rsc.org/en/content/articlelanding/2020/ee/c9ee03307f/unauth#!divAbstract</a></p>\n<p>在这项研究中，利用离子辐照的方法，基于其有可控照射面积、可调节照射剂量和可均匀辐照等特性，通过核能损失和电子能损失来改变材料的分子结构。高速的辐射离子可以剪切聚合物材料的化学键，旧化学键断裂而产生的大量自由基与运动离子结合，重新排列的形成了新的化学键和新的官能团，从而改变材料的起电性能。通过大量实验的筛选，找到合适的辐照计量和能量大小，可以从分子水平上直接控制和改变针对摩擦起电的聚合物官能团，进而永久的改变材料的起电特性。选择低能量的离子辐射,对目标聚合物的表面粗糙度和机械柔韧性的影响可忽略不计，同时可以永久的改变材料的起电性能，是一种全新的方法。</p>\n<link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"/css/spoiler.css\" type=\"text/css\"><script src=\"/js/spoiler.js\" type=\"text/javascript\" async></script>","text":" [Figure] 自2012年以来，摩擦电纳米发电机（TENG）由于其普遍适用性强，成本低，效率高逐渐成为机械能量收集和分布式微能源领域的主流技术。TENG的发展可以服务于物联网的信息采集技术、智能监控系统以及静电驱动、静电除尘等高电压应用领域。TENGs中的摩擦起电材料是决定","link":"","raw":null,"photos":[],"categories":[{"name":"Tech - Q","slug":"Tech-Q","count":2,"path":"api/categories/Tech-Q.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"KAPTON","slug":"KAPTON","count":1,"path":"api/tags/KAPTON.json"},{"name":"Radiation","slug":"Radiation","count":1,"path":"api/tags/Radiation.json"}]}]}